text: SY Lady of the Lake may refer to: *SY Lady of the Lake (1859), a vessel built in 1859 for service on Coniston Water in the English Lake District *SY Lady of the Lake (1877), a vessel built in 1877 for service on Ullswater in the English Lake District and since converted to the MY Lady of the Lake *SY Lady of the Lake (1908), a vessel built in 1908 to replace the 1859 vessel on Coniston Water in the English Lake District
title: SY Lady of the Lake
